OL,3,CHundreds attend service to mark 50
OL,4,Cyears since M62 coach bombing
OL,6,FHundreds of people have attended a
OL,7,F50th anniversary service to remember
OL,8,Fthe victims of an coach bombing in .
OL,10,FTwelve people, including two children,
OL,11,Fwere killed when a bomb exploded on a
OL,12,Fcoach carrying military personnel and
OL,13,Ftheir families on the M62 in February
OL,14,F1974.
OL,16,FTo mark 50 years since the bombing,
OL,17,Frelatives of those who died attended a
OL,18,Fparade, service and wreath-laying
OL,19,Fceremony at Hartshead Moor Services on
OL,20,FSunday morning.
