OL,6,FBombardier Terrence Griffin, who
OL,7,Fjoined the army when he was 15, was 24
OL,8,Fwhen he died in the coach bombing.
OL,10,FHis sister Mo Norton took part in the
OL,11,Fmemorial service and said the passing
OL,12,Fof 50 years since his death does not
OL,13,Fmake it easier to come to terms with.
