OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "I don't think it
OL,7,Fis any easier because it's with you
OL,8,Fall the time. When you lose other
OL,9,Fpeople you love through illness or
OL,10,Faccidents that's heartbreaking but
OL,11,Fbecause this was done on purpose and
OL,12,Fnobody was brought to justice, I don't
OL,13,Fthink it will ever leave me.
OL,15,F"Because I still miss him and I think
OL,16,Fabout him all the time."
