OL,6,FShe added: "For those you love around
OL,7,Fyou you've got to move forward and I
OL,8,Fjust think living in a civilised
OL,9,Fsociety we need to find the people who
OL,10,Fdo these things
OL,12,F"But I don't think that's going to
OL,13,Fhappen so I'm just here to remember
OL,14,FTerence really and just remember the
OL,15,Fgood times and hold on to that."
OL,17,FHundreds of people, including many
OL,18,Fmembers of the military community,
OL,19,Fturned up in the rain to pay their
OL,20,Frespects to the fallen.
