OL,4,Cyears since M62 coach bombing
OL,6,F17-year-old Signalman Leslie Walsh is
OL,7,Fone of those who died in the attack.
OL,9,FHis brother Albert Walsh said: "I'm
OL,10,Fone of five children and Leslie and I
OL,11,Fwere the closest in age. We grew up
OL,12,Ftogether, we shared bedrooms together
OL,13,Fwhen we were younger, we fought
OL,14,Ftogether, we were the closest. And I
OL,15,Ftook him to catch the coach on that
OL,16,Ffateful day.
