OL,6,F"It broke my mother's heart. My mum
OL,7,Fnever got over the fact that she lost
OL,8,Fher youngest child. Seventeen years
OL,9,Fold - shocking really. I'm now 70,
OL,10,FLesley would be 67, and you constantly
OL,11,Fthink: what would he be up to now?"
OL,13,FHe added: "I miss him. I miss him
OL,14,Fevery day."
OL,16,FThe families of the M62 coach bombing
OL,17,Fvictims will continue to meet for a
OL,18,Fmemorial service on the anniversary
OL,19,Feach year.
